<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SPORTMATCH — 요청 횟수 초과</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
<div class="error-page">
  <div class="error-bg-number">429</div>

  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center">
    <div class="error-emoji">⏳</div>
    <div class="error-code">429 · Too Many Requests</div>
    <div class="error-title">잠깐만요, 너무 빠르네요!</div>
    <div class="error-desc">
      짧은 시간 안에 너무 많은 요청이 들어왔어요.<br>
      잠시 후 다시 시도해 주세요.
    </div>
    <div class="error-actions">
      <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="back-btn">← 이전으로</a>
      <a href="/" class="back-btn">🏠 홈으로</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script>
  const initialSecs = parseInt(document.getElementById('countdown').textContent.trim()) || 60;
  document.getElementById('countdownBar').style.setProperty('--wait', initialSecs + 's');
  let secs = initialSecs;
  const timer = setInterval(() => {
    secs--;
    document.getElementById('countdown').textContent = secs;
    if (secs <= 0) {
      clearInterval(timer);
      document.getElementById('countdown').textContent = '0';
      location.reload();
    }
  }, 1000);
</script>
</body>
</html>
